## development


Launch configuration (./.vscode/launch.json):

	{
		"configurations": [
			{
				"name": "debug kvix gui",
				"type": "debugpy",
				"request": "launch",
				"program": "${workspaceFolder}/run.py",
				"justMyCode": false,
			}
		]
	}
